window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>March 15th, Earth Year 2290</b></p> <p><b>The day the aliens returned.</b></p> <p>The memories are still fresh.<br> Of colonies burning.<br> Of millions dying in agony.</p> <p>Fifty years later, we’ve built up our strength.<br> Using a wormhole, we colonized both sides of the galaxy.</p> <p>It was the worst mistake we could have made.<br> Our enemy has returned and the wormhole has collapsed.</p> <p>Commander Thatcher finds himself on the wrong side of the divide.<br> Separated from his pregnant wife by countless light years.</p> <p>He’s just been given command of a light armored cruiser.</p> <p>His first command.</p> <p>If he ever wants to see his wife again, he’ll need to do the impossible.<br> To defeat this enemy, he will need to reinvent space warfare.</p> <p>So that’s just what he’s going to do.</p> <p><b><i>Spacers</i></b><b> contains </b><b><i>First Command</i></b><b> through to the end of </b><b><i>Free Space.</i></b></p>"; 
